### Health Check
GET {{ChipmeoApis.Api_HostAddress}}/health

###############################################
# AUTHENTICATION
###############################################

### Login (Get JWT Token)
POST {{ChipmeoApis.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Logout
POST {{ChipmeoApis.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

